{"tid":561071,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"涉用假車牌佔用月租車位　41歲男警被捕","createTime":"2018-02-14T16:38:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-14T16:52:51.000Z","uid":35192,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"66f59e2e3bb2814beb94cdf40de78965412e077e","tid":561071,"uid":35192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T16:38:15.000Z","msg":"一名男警涉嫌於上月15日，以假車牌使用他人的月租車位，星期二（2月13日）被警方拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n警方港島總區刑事部展開調查之後，發現涉事的電單車，車主為一名41歲姓吳的男警，星期二以涉嫌「以欺騙手段取得財產」罪名，將男警拘捕，他已獲准保釋，本月下旬再向警方報到，案件由港島總區重案組跟進。"},{"pid":"1dc665539b2fb08dd1232e047264670e1139802c","tid":561071,"uid":4525,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T16:39:51.000Z","msg":"少左段野"},{"pid":"d8fc0288821142defb74484a621e812f744dfff5","tid":561071,"uid":53568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1dc665539b2fb08dd1232e047264670e1139802c","tid":561071,"uid":4525,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T16:39:51.000Z","msg":"少左段野"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T16:41:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb3df38b2c569053af7959580b9e85fe757abf23","tid":561071,"uid":35192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T16:52:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}